License for Story2Belief has not yet been chosen. Candidates under consideration:

- MIT — permissive, simple, common for research code.
- Apache-2.0 — permissive with explicit patent grant.
- CC-BY-4.0 — for documentation and data, not code.
- Dual: MIT for code in src/, CC-BY-4.0 for docs/ and any bundled corpora.

Until a license is chosen, all rights are reserved by the author.

Replace the contents of this file with the chosen license text once a decision
is made (and record the decision as an ADR in docs/decisions/).
